(8, 'Greek Farro Salad', 250, 200, '1557897418-greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-768x1151.jpg', '<div class=\"cookbook-promo\">\r\n<section id=\"custom_html-7\" class=\"widget_text widget widget_custom_html\">\r\n<div class=\"widget_text widget-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"textwidget custom-html-widget\">Our cookbook, Love Real Food, is here! <a href=\"https://amzn.to/2SDbeut\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get your copy</a> ↣<img src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2017/05/love-real-food-150.png\" alt=\"Love Real Food\" data-pin-nopin=\"true\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2017/05/love-real-food-150.png\" class=\"lazyloaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"64\" height=\"75\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-sidebar-wrap\"><main class=\"content\">\r\n<article class=\"post-17682 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-easy-weeknight-dinners category-egg-free-lactovegetarian category-fall category-entrees category-greek-vegetarian-recipes category-nut-free category-pack-for-lunch category-food-recipes category-salads category-side-dishes category-soy-free category-spring category-summer category-tomato-free category-winter tag-arugula tag-bean-salad tag-chickpeas tag-cucumber tag-farro tag-olives tag-parsley tag-roasted-red-peppers entry\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/CreativeWork\"><header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\" itemprop=\"headline\">Greek Farro Salad</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\">\r\n<p class=\"entry-meta\"><span class=\"entry-comments-link\"><a href=\"https://cookieandkate.com/greek-farro-salad-recipe/#comments\">83 Comments</a></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"tasty-recipes-quick-links\"><a class=\"tasty-recipes-jump-link\" href=\"https://cookieandkate.com/greek-farro-salad-recipe/#tasty-recipes-23946\">Jump to Recipe</a></div>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-30342 size-full lazyloaded\" src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4.jpg\" alt=\"Greek farro salad recipe\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4.jpg 1100w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-550x824.jpg 550w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-270x405.jpg 270w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-768x1151.jpg 768w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 90vw, (max-width: 865px) 80vw, 550px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 90vw, (max-width: 865px) 80vw, 550px\" srcset=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4.jpg 1100w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-550x824.jpg 550w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-270x405.jpg 270w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/greek-farro-salad-recipe-4-768x1151.jpg 768w\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"1100\" height=\"1648\"></p>\r\n<p>Sometimes recipe concepts sit on my list for months, waiting to be made. Sometimes a craving strikes and a corresponding recipe materializes out of thin air—such is the case with this Greek farro salad. It features bold Mediterranean flavors (lemon, herbs, chickpeas, roasted red peppers and feta), tossed with lots of fresh, peppery arugula and warm, chewy whole grains. Pass me a fork already!</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17690 lazyloaded\" src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2015/09/ingredients.jpg\" alt=\"ingredients\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2015/09/ingredients.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"550\" height=\"378\"></p>\r\n<p>The best part? This salad keeps well for two to three days in the fridge, which is always welcome, but especially right now. The seasons are changing here in Kansas City and it’s just too nice outside to stay inside and cook. Let’s soak up all the seventy-degree days we can get!</p>\r\n<div class=\"adthrive-player-container adthrive-collapse-player\" id=\"adthrive-collapse-container\" style=\"height: 330px;\">\r\n<div class=\"adthrive-player-position adthrive-collapse-sticky\" id=\"adthrive-collapse-position\" style=\"left: 929.6px; width: 300px; top: 0px;\">\r\n<div class=\"adthrive-player-close\" style=\"display: flex;\" id=\"adthrive-collapse-close\"><span>close</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</main></div>\r\n<p>To that end, I’m keeping this post short and sweet. Do let me know how you like this salad—please comment below and post a photo to Instagram with the hashtag <a href=\"https://instagram.com/explore/tags/cookieandkate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#cookieandkate</a>! I always want to hear/see how my recipes turn out for you.</p>\r\n<p><span id=\"more-17682\"></span><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-30345 size-full lazyloaded\" src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives.jpg\" alt=\"roasted red pepper, olives and cucumber\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives.jpg 1100w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-550x400.jpg 550w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-270x196.jpg 270w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-768x558.jpg 768w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 90vw, (max-width: 865px) 80vw, 550px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 90vw, (max-width: 865px) 80vw, 550px\" srcset=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives.jpg 1100w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-550x400.jpg 550w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-270x196.jpg 270w, https://cookieandkate.com/images/2018/08/cucumber-chickpeas-olives-768x558.jpg 768w\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"1100\" height=\"799\"></p>', 1),
(9, 'Chickpea Salad with Herbed Yogurt', 350, 300, '1557897492-farro-and-cucumber.jpg', '<p>I have news. No, I didn’t get a promotion. No, I’m not moving (yet). No, I’m not engaged (hahaaa). Are you ready for this? I got a dishwasher! Found him on craigslist, a portable Whirlpool, and he’s the most beautiful hunk of metal I’ve ever seen. I only wish we had met sooner, because washing dishes by hand has been the bane of my existence over the past year. You can reasonably expect more recipes to come out of <a href=\"http://instagram.com/p/cZX9A6FkoM/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">my tiny kitchen</a> now that I have his help.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8737 lazyloaded\" src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2013/07/farro-and-cucumber.jpg\" alt=\"farro and cucumber\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2013/07/farro-and-cucumber.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"550\" height=\"378\"></p>\r\n<p>This recipe is our first collaboration. It’s a Greek salad featuring warm farro, chickpeas and crisp, garden-fresh cucumber courtesy of <a href=\"http://bigeatstinykitchen.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">my friend Alissa</a>. The salad is sort of a deconstructed, abstract falafel sandwich (it’s not too far off from last summer’s <a href=\"https://cookieandkate.com/2012/baked-falafel/\">falafel salad</a>). Whole chickpeas take the place of the falafel, warm whole grain farro replaces the pita, and the herbed yogurt is tzatziki inspired. It’s simple and full of bright flavors,</p>', 1),
(10, 'Lebanese Lemon-Parsley Bean Salad', 150, 120, '1557897727-salad-hat-chia.jpg', '<a class=\"tasty-recipes-jump-link\" href=\"https://cookieandkate.com/lemon-parsley-bean-salad-and-hummus/#tasty-recipes-23454\">p</a>I worked in a dreadful office environment for a while. By “a while,” I mean 565 loooong days. Some days, I watched the sunrise and sunset through my car windows during my stop-and-go highway commute. Maybe you know how that goes. Maybe you’re reading this from a similarly dreadful office environment. If so, I feel for you.\r\n<div class=\"content-sidebar-wrap\"><main class=\"content\">\r\n<article class=\"post-8897 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-appetizers category-budget-friendly category-vegetarian-christmas-recipes category-dairy-free category-egg-free-lactovegetarian category-gluten-free category-vegetarian-lebanese-recipes category-greek-vegetarian-recipes category-pack-for-lunch category-food-recipes category-salads category-side-dishes category-healthy-snacks category-soy-free category-summer category-vegetarian-thanksgiving-recipes category-tomato-free category-vegan tag-bean-salad tag-celery tag-chickpeas tag-cucumber tag-dill tag-hummus tag-kidney-beans tag-lemon tag-mint tag-parsley tag-tahini tag-tomatoes entry\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/CreativeWork\">\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\">\r\n<p>Anyway, every day upon arrival, I plunked down at my desk with my big mug of coffee and started counting down the minutes until lunchtime. I usually brought my own lunch to save money, but some days I just had to escape the office and find refuge in a restaurant. I’m not sure I would have made it through those days without a good lunch.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8916 lazyloaded\" src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2013/08/homemade-hummus-and-pita-chips-2.jpg\" alt=\"homemade hummus and pita chips\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cookieandkate.com/images/2013/08/homemade-hummus-and-pita-chips-2.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" width=\"550\" height=\"378\"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</main></div>', 1),
(11, 'Cherry red CANADA', 300, 250, '1557898152-trai-cay-nhap-khau-trai-cherry-1.jpg', '<p>Trái Cherry là loại trái cây nhập khẩu sạch, rất ngon miệng và có giá trị dinh dưỡng rất cao. Do đó giá bán Cherry thường không rẻ nên trái Cherry thường được dùng làm quà biếu, quà tặng Tết.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://bizweb.dktcdn.net/100/083/428/files/trai-cay-nhap-khau-trai-cherry-1.jpg?v=1465956163372\"></p>\r\n<p>Ngoài ra, trái Cherry không chỉ là một loại thực phẩm ngon miệng mà còn là bí quyết làm đẹp của nhiều chị em phụ nữ do chứa nhiều Vitamin A, Vitamin C, chất chống Ôxy hóa, và Collagen giúp da đàn hồi và săn chắc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://bizweb.dktcdn.net/100/083/428/files/trai-cay-nhap-khau-trai-cherry-2.jpg?v=1465956222410\"></p>\r\n<p>Đặc biệt, Trái Cherry là một trong những loại trái cây tốt cho bà bầu để bổ sung Vitamin và khoáng chất.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br> <img src=\"http://bizweb.dktcdn.net/100/083/428/files/trai-cay-nhap-khau-trai-cherry-3.jpg?v=1465956345593\"></p>\r\n<p>DNTN Rau Quả Bình Thuận chuyên về trái cây nhập khẩu, là đơn vị nhập khẩu trực tiếp và phân phối loại hoa quả nhập khẩu này. Doanh nghiệp nhập trái cây trực tiếp từ Mỹ, Canada và phân phối tại khắp các thành phố lớn trong cả nước với giá cả cạnh tranh nhất.</p>', 2);

